lines.text: I've been listening to you for so long. I'm so sick of you. Do you really think you can drive me into a corner? Who do you think you are? Scum who imagines itself human. You betray each other for your own benefit, you are capable of humiliating others, of trampling and destroying anyone who stands in your way. I despise you. I do not want to see you. Ever again. I want you to know that I'd rather die than give you the key. I'm so tired of you. Get out of my house.
lines.character: Yelena Sergeyevna, the teacher of mathematics

lines.text: Take the key. It's in your pocket. On the bond together with the door
